Package: LangVizPhylo
Type: Application
Title: Phylogenetic Analysis Service for LangViz
Version: 0.1.0
Author: LangViz Team
Description: JSON-RPC server providing phylogenetic tree inference,
    bootstrap analysis, and hierarchical clustering for linguistic data.
    Uses ape and phangorn for rigorous statistical methods.
License: MIT
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0),
    ape (>= 5.7),
    phangorn (>= 2.11.0),
    pvclust (>= 2.2-0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)

